=============================
=  README for Ex6  =
=============================
usage:
java GameController

==================
=  Description:  =
==================
Ball class:
creating and handeling a ball, controll its direction and speed.

Paddle class:
creating and handeling the lower paddle, enabling it to move right or left, bouncing the ball if hit.

Brick class:
creating, handeling and disappering bricks (and the walls). bouncing the ball if hit.

Game class:
main class, creating and handeling the rest of the classes. painting the window and handeling time quants.



